1. What problem CI/CD solves

Developers write code daily

Manual testing is slow

Manual deployment causes mistakes

Bugs reach users

CI/CD automates testing and deployment

‚≠ê CI/CD removes manual errors and saves time

‚≠ê 2. CI/CD in one simple line

CI/CD is an automatic system

It checks your code

It safely delivers it to users

‚≠ê Easy line to remember:
‚≠ê CI/CD checks and delivers code automatically

‚≠ê 3. CI/CD has two main parts

CI ‚Äì Continuous Integration

CD ‚Äì Continuous Delivery / Deployment

‚≠ê 4. Real-world example (Pizza shop üçï)

You = Developer

Pizza = Code

